article_text:
NextEra Energy Inc. on Monday reported a better-than-expected 8.2% increase in revenue in its second quarter, while the company raised a long-term earnings forecast.

Meanwhile, affiliate company NextEra Energy Partners LP said it has agreed to buy privately held NET Midstream in a $2.1 billion deal.
